Package com.poesys.ms.col

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IColumnValue<T>
    A column value is a serializable, single-valued, named data item of a specific data type, with the type specified through an enumerated set of supported types.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColumnValueImpl<T>
    An implementation of the IColumnValue interface that represents a column value of a specific data type.
    ColumnValueImplTest
    Tests the methods on the interface implementation ColumnValueImpl
    NullColumnValueImpl
    An implementation of the IColumnValue interface that represents a null column value that has a specific JDBC data type.
    NullColumnValueImplTest
    Tests the methods on the interface implementation NullColumnValueImpl
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IColumnValue.ColumnType
    The column type type
